    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean, i know you're saying i should focus on myself, but that's the thing. there's nothing left of \"me\" to focus on. everything i am is just a target for people to hate or misunderstand. it feels like the only way to actually be at peace and stop the noise is to just... not be here. does that even make sense? like, is it crazy to feel like the fight just isn't worth the cost anymore?",
